cc:Work.dc:description: The BMW 328 is a sports car made between 1936 and 1940. It featured many advanced features for its time, such as a tubular space frame and a hemispherical combustion chamber engine \n______________________________________ \n(Wikipedia - http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BMW_328)
